      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "INSPECTION (1) finished in the placings last time but could not have been more impressive before that in his quick 25.89 win at Geelong over 460m. Hot win two back and looks the one to beat here. MAGIC BOCCA (5) is progressing well claiming her 2nd career win latest, scoring by 7 lengths (25.38) at Warrnambool. Strong form has emerged from her last run. Can measure up again. REINDEER KEITH (6) continues to race well but is struggling to break through, placing at his last four runs. Last time finished 2nd in a Mix 6/7 FIN on March 7 over 525m at this track behind Uncle Stiltskin beaten 8 lengths (30.62). Some good form is emerging from his last run. Likely to be in the finish again. LADY RAPID (2) is a last start winner who rates one of the chances again.",
